it trails for compliance"}],""]}],["$","p","337",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["✅ ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Real-time policy enforcement"}],""]}],["$","p","338",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["✅ ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Integration with existing CI/CD and approval tools"}],""]}],["$","br","339",{}],["$","p","340",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Don't let your organization become the next cautionary tale. The question isn't whether you'll experience an AI incident—it's whether you'll implement governance before or after it happens."]}],["$","br","341",{}],["$","p","342",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*Ready to prevent your first AI incident?*"}],["$","br","343",{}],["$","p","344",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["🔗 ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Start Free:"}]," [regulator.ai/try](https://regulator.ai/try)"]}],["$","p","345",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["💻 ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Demo:"}]," See execution control in action"]}],["$","p","346",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["📖 ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Documentation:"}]," Complete setup guide"]}],["$","p","347",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["💬 ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Support:"}]," Get help implementing governance"]}],["$","br","348",{}],["$","hr","349",{"className":"border-navy-700 my-8"}],["$","br","350",{}],["$","p","351",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*About the Author*"}],["$","br","352",{}],["$","p","353",{